                    <p>Referring to the function in <xref ref="figure-discontinuities"/>, decide whether each of the following statements are true or false.</p>
                </statement>
            </introduction>
            <exercise>
                <statement>
                    <p><m>h</m> is continuous on <m>\cointerval{-4}{-1}</m>.</p>
                </statement> 
            </exercise>
            <exercise>
