        <exercisegroup> 
            <introduction>
                <p>Several functions are described below. Your task is to draw each function on its provided axis system. Do not introduce any unnecessary discontinuities or intercepts that are not directly implied by the stated properties. Make sure that you draw all implied asymptotes and label them with their equations.</p>
